           <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n师资队伍</div>\n                <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">        \n                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资队伍</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资信息</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1/rngcyjs1/ALL.htm\">ALL</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"\">正文</a>\n</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"clearfix \">\n                             <ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\"><li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资信息</a></li>\n                    \n<li><a href=\"../../szdw/ltxjs.htm\">离退休教师</a></li>\n                    \n</ul>\n            </div>\n        </div> </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n                 <ul class=\"banner-ul pull-right tabs-ul clearfix wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\"></ul>\n        </div>\n      \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/jquery/jquery-latest.min.js\"></script>\n <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/6/73/95/5A0B9586F3E062523593AF1E685_56AF5516_2350.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>司桐</a>助理研究员</div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                        <p>办公电话：010-62782108</p>\n                        <p>电子邮箱：sitong@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                        <p>通讯地址：北京市海淀区东升镇双清综合楼A座354</p>\n                        <p>邮编：100084</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n\n    <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"sz\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n <strong>教育背景</strong>\n</div>\n<p>2017.09-2021.06 华北电力大学（热能工程）工学博士</p>\n<p>2011.09-2015.06 华北电力大学（热能与动力工程）工学学士</p>\n<div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n <strong>工作履历</strong>\n</div>\n<p>2025.03至今 清华大学能动系 助理研究员</p>\n<p>2022.03-2025.02 清华大学能动系 博士后</p>\n<p>2021.07-2022.01 华北电力大学动力工程系 讲师</p>\n<h4>\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  学术兼职\n </div></h4>\n<p>国际燃烧学会会员</p>\n<p>中国电机工程学会会员</p>\n<div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n <strong>研究领域</strong>\n</div>\n<p>化石燃料掺氢/氨高效清洁燃烧技术、金属燃烧等</p>\n<h4>\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  研究概况\n </div></h4>\n<p><b>在研科研项目</b></p>\n<p>1. 水蒸气效应对氨-煤共燃过程中燃烧特性与污染物生成作用机理研究 国家自然科学基金青年基金 项目负责人</p>\n<p>2. 煤粉炉掺烧低碳/零碳燃料源头降碳技术研究 国家重点研发计划项目 子课题负责人</p>\n<p>3. 氨/煤掺烧低碳清洁高效燃烧技术研发及中试应用验证 企事业委托项目 项目负责人</p>\n<p>4. 掺氢/氨燃气清洁高效燃烧关键技术 国家重点研发计划项目 课题骨干</p>\n<p>5. 火电厂掺烧低碳燃料灵活运行分析模型与软件开发 企事业委托项目 课题骨干</p>\n<p><b>已完成科研项目</b></p>\n<p>1. 高湿环境下氨-煤粉燃烧过程中NOx生成机理及调控研究 中国博士后第73批科学基金 项目负责人</p>\n<p>2. 掺氢天然气微混低氮燃烧技术研究 企事业委托项目 课题骨干</p>\n<p>3. 燃煤锅炉污染物（SO2、NOx、PM）一体化控制技术研究及工程示范 国家重点研发计划项目 课题骨干</p>\n<h4>\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  奖励与荣誉\n </div></h4>\n<p>河北省优秀博士论文（2022）北京市优秀毕业生（2021）、国家奖学金（2020）</p>\n<h4>\n <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n  学术成果\n </div><p>发表SCI收录论文10余篇，发表于Proc. Combust. Inst、Applied Energy、Fuel、Chem. Eng. J.、Energy等国际权威期刊，申请或授权发明专利8项，授权美国专利1项。</p></h4></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n    \n\n</form>\n\n    </div>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  <div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container clearfix\">\n     <div class=\"footer-l\">\n              <div class=\"footer-logo\">    \n    <a href=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wbimage&quot;, 1692924305, 59340)\"><img src=\"../../images/dblogo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"imgInline\"></a>\n</div>\n            <div class=\"footer-copyright f16\">\n                <!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>地址：北京市海淀区清华园1号 100084，电话：010-62782508</p><p>Copyright © 2024 清华大学 All Rights Reserved</p>\n            </div>\n\n      </div> \n      \n      \n      <div class=\"footer-link\">\n            <dl>\n                  <dt class=\"f28\">友情链接</dt>\n                 \n <dd class=\"f16\"><a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1692924305, 69331)\">清华大学</a></dd>\n <dd class=\"f16\"><a href=\"http://tspe.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1692924305, 69332)\">热科学与动力工程教育部重点实验室</a></dd>\n\n            </dl>\n      </div>\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"footer-r\">\n     <ul>\n          \n    \n<li><a href=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wbimage&quot;, 1692924305, 59342)\"><img src=\"../../images/qinghuadaxuenengyuanyudongligongchengxierweima.jpg\"></a><p>官方微信</p></li>\n\n\n      </ul>\n      \n      </div>\n      \n      \n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n<script src=\"../../js/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/bootstrap.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/slick.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/wow.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/common.js\"></script>\n<script>\nif (!(/msie [6|7|8|9]/i.test(navigator.userAgent))){\n  new WOW